.TH "dwc2_hsotg_wait_bit_clear" 9 "dwc2_hsotg_wait_bit_clear" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dwc2_hsotg_wait_bit_clear \- Waits for bit to be clear.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" dwc2_hsotg_wait_bit_clear
.BI "(struct dwc2_hsotg *hsotg "  ","
.BI "u32 offset "  ","
.BI "u32 mask "  ","
.BI "u32 timeout "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hsotg" 12
Programming view of DWC_otg controller.
.IP "offset" 12
Register's offset where bit/bits must be set.
.IP "mask" 12
Mask of the bit/bits which must be set.
.IP "timeout" 12
Timeout to wait.
.SH "RETURN"
0 if bit/bits are set or -ETIMEDOUT in case of timeout.
